        "created_at": "2022-07-23T16:57:35.000Z",
        "cooked": "<aside class=\"quote no-group\" data-post=\"2\" data-topic=\"284380\">\n<blockquote>\n<p>Thanks for the note.  Sommselect has this on offer today and I was thinking about purchasing a few bottles\u2013curiously they list the alcohol at 13%.  WS has it at 13.8%, and I can\u2019t seem to find a tech sheet with the official listing.</p>\n</blockquote>\n</aside>\n<p>Yeah, I saw that. Don\u2019t know what to make of it. All I know is that the back of the label on my Skurnik imported bottles note 14.5%<br>\n<div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"/uploads/db3686/original/3X/b/c/bcb8aba37aca42cc781929c27638c3142cd2433f.jpeg\" data-download-href=\"https://www.wineberserkers.com/uploads/db0731/bcb8aba37aca42cc781929c27638c3142cd2433f\" title=\"IMG_0778.jpeg\"><img src=\"https://www.wineberserkers.com/uploads/db0731/optimized/3X/b/c/bcb8aba37aca42cc781929c27638c3142cd2433f_2_666x500.jpeg\" alt=\"IMG_0778.jpeg\" data-base62-sha1=\"qVvpYYdg6uJcL5CsMqwKtym0f2D\" width=\"666\" height=\"500\" srcset=\"https://www.wineberserkers.com/uploads/db0731/optimized/3X/b/c/bcb8aba37aca42cc781929c27638c3142cd2433f_2_666x500.jpeg, https://www.wineberserkers.com/uploads/db0731/optimized/3X/b/c/bcb8aba37aca42cc781929c27638c3142cd2433f_2_999x750.jpeg 1.5x, https://www.wineberserkers.com/uploads/db0731/optimized/3X/b/c/bcb8aba37aca42cc781929c27638c3142cd2433f_2_1332x1000.jpeg 2x\" data-dominant-color=\"7F766E\"><div class=\"meta\"><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-far-image svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#far-image\"></use></svg><span class=\"filename\">IMG_0778.jpeg</span><span class=\"informations\">4032\u00d73024 1.39 MB</span><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-discourse-expand svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#discourse-expand\"></use></svg></div></a></div></p>",
